ActDepartment of Human Resources and Skills Development Act
PrecisAppointment of JANICE CHARETTE of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Deputy Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development, to be styled Deputy Minister of Human Resources and Social Development, to hold office during pleasure; and appointment of JANICE CHARETTE as a commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission, to be the Chairperson of the Commission; effective July 1, 2006.
